 />"},{"pid":"678f1d2602ce02247bd0b2691c30c8de6c2f83f9","tid":1398502,"uid":128472,"like":162,"dislike":3,"score":159,"quote":{"pid":"df2b25dbee005c895d5c4efd61d3da8861877ac7","tid":1398502,"uid":2419,"like":259,"dislike":3,"score":256,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T21:41:39.000Z","msg":"如果真係唔岩做 用呢份人工跳出去都易行好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T21:48:11.000Z","msg":"睇嚟大家都覺得錢&gt;一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得我呢啲入世未深既細蚊仔咁介懷人哋目光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35edc6f635013168949ae036581fe60bb6ee83be","tid":1398502,"uid":290754,"like":79,"dislike":8,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T21:57:22.000Z","msg":"出嚟做嘢最緊要<br />\n《唔做屋企人介紹同嘅工》<br />\n<br />\n基本上做得好都只會歸功俾你屋企人，做得差嘅話更加會怪你屋企人，人唔會睇到你真正嘅實力。咁樣對你嘅能力自己評估自己同埋人哋評估你都係唔公平，咁點解要俾個陷阱你自己同埋你嘅屋企人？其實介紹人同比介紹姐都存在好大壓力。一定要搵到一個舞台俾自己係自己建立比自己嘅！加油"},{"pid":"08981d7c13c124a213a11a7e57a3116414a7367e","tid":1398502,"uid":59955,"like":145,"dislike":4,"score":141,"quote":{"pid":"678f1d2602ce02247bd0b2691c30c8de6c2f83f9","tid":1398502,"uid":128472,"like":162,"dislike":3,"score":159,"quote":{"pid":"df2b25dbee005c895d5c4efd61d3da8861877ac7","tid":1398502,"uid":2419,"like":259,"dislike":3,"score":256,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T21:41:39.000Z","msg":"如果真係唔岩做 用呢份人工跳出去都易行好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T21:48:11.000Z","msg":"睇嚟大家都覺得錢&gt;一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得我呢啲入世未深既細蚊仔咁介懷人哋目光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T22:27:43.000Z","msg":"少5千就係少5千 返工都係為出糧 錢行頭<br />\n何況做落到時真係唔岩既<br />\n你起碼叫有經驗 跳出去都嗌得返呢個價"},{"pid":"43f3bee20db6a7cd997847209e8922251b397925","tid":1398502,"uid":122853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T23:58:04.000Z","msg":"要預左比其他人話你係裙腳仔，暗地裡一定會咁講"},{"pid":"4df5