{"pid":"1ab3146035e9ab5b39fced5cac065cc8e3b2ab7c","tid":1398502,"uid":92479,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T00:14:36.000Z","msg":"唔比人知又得唔得，啲高層鍾意擺卧底係公司"},{"pid":"73437be95d361fbc9e83a6fce4f1e080b6ba1480","tid":1398502,"uid":156751,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"quote":{"pid":"678f1d2602ce02247bd0b2691c30c8de6c2f83f9","tid":1398502,"uid":128472,"like":162,"dislike":3,"score":159,"quote":{"pid":"df2b25dbee005c895d5c4efd61d3da8861877ac7","tid":1398502,"uid":2419,"like":259,"dislike":3,"score":256,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T21:41:39.000Z","msg":"如果真係唔岩做 用呢份人工跳出去都易行好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T21:48:11.000Z","msg":"睇嚟大家都覺得錢&gt;一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得我呢啲入世未深既細蚊仔咁介懷人哋目光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T00:15:05.000Z","msg":"返工唔為錢返乜柒工"},{"pid":"fe7ee6d22119cfbdcb5e66791bc703e7373d2a99","tid":1398502,"uid":87780,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T00:17:27.000Z","msg":"日日同媽咪食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb727ab0bf95f4d66e99e9d830618467bd53560","tid":1398502,"uid":62837,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T00:20:10.000Z","msg":"俾人話群腳咪群腳 <br />\n其實你個人做到野咪得<br />\n唔係係乜都阿媽阿媽<br />\n有自己獨立能力咪唔會俾人話"},{"pid":"405bb7ac9265661f89d1ea9a0e4c14f3c5d1fa3e","tid":1398502,"uid":29879,"like":89,"dislike":1,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T00:21:33.000Z","msg":"有後門都唔走 直頭叫on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你洗鳩理人諗咩<br />\n做左先諗， 你阿媽應該有番咁上下人脈<br />\n唔係點開呢個後門比你<br />\n其實你可以放心， 香港人無咁得閒理隔離果個係點入黎， 佢地只會計較邊個人工高d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f7efb7e99485459e2fc3949d4df2b135fe2835","tid":1398502,"uid":48151,"like":45,"dislike":5,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"6c5a8339d6c7b80c24a743efebb1c1cb63bc8b46","tid":1398502,"uid":128472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T21:36:24.000Z","msg":"2019 fresh grad未開始搵工。咁老母今日同我講話佢公司有個人就走，就問我要唔要入去做。個職位本身淨係請有經驗既人，所以其實我都好驚入咗去但根本冇能力勝任，會唔心安理得同埋影衰老母。加上同自己阿媽同一間公司，所有嘢好似會變得好奇怪同柒（雖然唔同department）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lunch一齊/唔一齊食好奇怪，當私人時間同自己阿媽傾公事又係唔知想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋入到去應該會有閒言閒語（已經想像到比人恥笑靠母幹、裙腳仔）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但個職位應該幾好pay，如果我用自己能力喺出面搵應該會少成5k人工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請問如果係你哋會點揀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T00:22:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認真回你</span><br />\n<br />\n高5K請你？<br />\n你老細同你老母有路架？<br />\n<br />\n嗱，比個建議你<br />\n得閒去老細房執下頭髮<br />\n同自己對比下DNA<br />\n可能有驚人發現"},{"pid":"a561c805015c87c4d3900ebf8a7efbddca3c9b32","tid":1398502,"uid":218318,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T00:24:23.000Z","msg":"唔使唔好意思，成功靠父(母)幹幾時都一樣，連Bill Gate都係靠老母先上到位，有乜唔好意思？<br />\n<br />\n好多人話無錢有乜資格生仔，我就話錢唔重要，無能力幫仔女拉人脈先至唔好學人生仔"},{"pid":"d6f1f3143aa0e88118980e31a001108f8ba69774","tid":1398502,"uid":126736,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T00:37:48.000Z","msg":"有邊個成功人士冇靠關係去起步<br />\n<br />\n唔take 你就後悔<br />\n<br />\n再者你阿媽都叫你去 我唔覺份工係真係technical 到要夠哂經驗先做得起<br />\n<br />\n你有唔明返屋企又有老母教你 <br />\n<br />\n俾盡你3 個月咪又係上到手"},{"pid":"7d3c157131b592328cae27268e1d75fa0a44a2c0","tid":1398502,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T00:39:00.000Z","msg":"請左你先算啦"},{"pid":"f7d6206dffa5e6bcfb6687bc528ac0cc229cd018","t