kgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n靠母幹、裙腳仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好PAY咪得囉,你理得人姐"},{"pid":"a00d2aa9c6a727441c6f035b981569a1659ae2c0","tid":1398502,"uid":22762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T01:54:29.000Z","msg":"怪唔知你叫尷尬發射站<br />\n我見到你嘅思路都為你人生感到尷尬<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗到你嘅出現，你嘅入職會令人高度關注<br />\n最重要係你做事能力<br />\n英雄莫問出處<br />\n你正正經經番工學野認真工作咪得囉<br />\n<br />\n你自己又驚比人話靠關係話裙腳<br />\n但又調番轉問人係咪要隠藏關係<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔虛心學習 去令自己對得住呢份人工<br />\n再加上有乜事就喺公司搵老母求救 唔學獨立<br />\n<br />\n你咪會變比人背後笑同廢事理你嗰d裙腳仔囉<br />\n大個仔喇好無"},{"pid":"bf655f7fa4ddf14b48329e7688166082ac3e6b39","tid":1398502,"uid":9726,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T01:55:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25383f1bb3d53618818a92324a0e4ffad10b9a47","tid":1398502,"uid":279963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T01:56:30.000Z","msg":"有咩事畀老頂鬧仲可以話:&quot;我要話畀媽咪聽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&quot;<br />\n咁先係裙腳仔o既極致"},{"pid":"6f765f777ddb4ab0d340821b92e8e28de70b7d01","tid":1398502,"uid":146636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T01:57:21.000Z","msg":"除非你其他一份工都搵唔到，唔係老西都唔好做<br />\n群腳仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea07d9c7ebaacee1f392e77af3c3299bbf22fd74","tid":1398502,"uid":119996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T01:59:55.000Z","msg":"有得老豆老母照住唔知幾幸福<br />\n人地講兩句你冇左忽肉？"},{"pid":"d84f31a16667a31f6ba5494d492ef6683320054e","tid":1398502,"uid":128472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a00d2aa9c6a727441c6f035b981569a1659ae2c0","tid":1398502,"uid":22762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T01:54:29.000Z","msg":"怪唔知你叫尷尬發射站<br />\n我見到你嘅思路都為你人生感到尷尬<br />\n<br />\n唔好