能力都要做 反正帶左老母返工"},{"pid":"d17c7705414cdfeb8dd5c5c1bd1c7d8f603284c6","tid":1398502,"uid":128472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75013d437f1dad5d9f168f56ffb81d0561fd1b4e","tid":1398502,"uid":1208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T01:51:17.000Z","msg":"同佢講唔好公開你地關係咪得<br />\n不過老母多數大喇叭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:04:29.000Z","msg":"如果叫佢唔好講，佢應該會話：怕咩畀人知！去到邊有冇人介紹都有人事關係。"},{"pid":"26cc7f35be96acaf6c9a70ff935d7f8ed3d0fd8d","tid":1398502,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c0fb3df8ae963a10ad320cc3a9903251efc821a","tid":1398502,"uid":56204,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"08193d3a8383a21a4ef04ae4205b2aa738daed38","tid":1398502,"uid":128472,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"772cba5f14adba4c4faeccf5a2e3223a9ee3b719","tid":1398502,"uid":56204,"like":13,"dislike":53,"score":-40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T00:13:03.000Z","msg":"舊公司有條仔做緊audit assistant，得個中七畢業，其他人全部accounting degree，佢老母係hr manager，我地日日笑9佢裙腳仔，由佢自生自滅，無人同佢食飯講野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T00:49:22.000Z","msg":"個audit仔好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T00:53:40.000Z","msg":"有咩咁慘，一個人去到個唔適合既環境就係咁架啦，根本書都未讀得成，英文又差，得d中學會計知識點做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:04:42.000Z","msg":"錯在幫佢搵Audit assistant<br />\n如果係OA根本冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62aa1e1286b4a2f677c07002e5f274506d0cf5f6","tid":1398502,"uid":128472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d91224e2fbeb950935bae651fbf880cefaeaf341","tid":1398502,"uid":6778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:00:42.000Z","msg":"個個當你狗咁撚 , 肯定比屎你食 陰鳩你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:05:09.000Z","msg":"最壞打算真係畀人辦公室欺凌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8690ea8df02b771c0d1b6102896b70a1f67e2f8","tid":1398502,"uid":39049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:12:38.000Z","msg":"喺屋企已經俾老母管住晒, 返到公司仲要俾老母管? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老母喺公司做咩post 先? 如果喺斟茶清潔呀姐就算吧啦.<br />\n<br />\n除非佢係老細, 你係太子仔, 否則都係咪搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c40793146e3308db54e7e4890fa10a472e63894","tid":1398502,"uid":39049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:13:49.000Z","msg":"喺屋企已經俾老母管住晒, 返到公司仲要俾老母管? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老母喺公司做咩post 先? 如果係斟茶清潔呀姐就算吧啦.<br />\n<br />\n除非佢係老細, 你係太子仔, 否則都係咪搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7270d7a62e6344bb2b023f1a740fc67942ed3949","tid":1398502,"uid":92275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:16:23.000Z","msg":"不知幾多人想有後門走, 珍惜機會, 唔識未學到識囉"},{"pid":"d930504742ba49ee2d4df1211fc08779544a6d0f","tid":1398502,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:16:30.000Z","msg":"唔好比人知咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你會將人際關係表貼係個頭到周圍行既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896cfaf005f0bd440df75e1650570efb59d5c9b2","tid":1398502,"uid":244361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:20:15.000Z","msg":"唔好只睇錢，要考慮兩樣嘢：<br />\n<br />\n第一，份工你係咪有興趣同有冇信心可以勝任，如果冇，你會好難捱，同事見你冇能力只靠關係，亦可能排擠你，日子會好難過<br />\n<br />\n第二，要睇吓你同伯母會唔會工作上有interaction，有嘅話其實幾尷尬，又可能有磨擦，返到屋企面左左就無謂啦"},{"pid":"659d791bac84ebd81feb18be940e680bf6206528","tid":1398502,"uid":38946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:21:50.000Z","msg":"公司大把廢人老屎忽<br />\n不過同老母同公司好撚老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01204a76f3e7faabcb9f5316e97596e2759e4d55","tid":1398502,"uid":179288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:23:22.000Z","msg":"你不如問你呀媽 <br />\n如果有個同事 一睇就知唔夠料坐呢個位<br />\n係走後門入黎做 佢會覺得點<br />\n<br />\n事實上好多人係靠關係入公司 <br />\n但當你靠完關係 又無個個能力 <br />\n除非你個位係junior <br />\n如果唔係你都唔洗指意<br />\n其他同事會教你野 同你食飯 <br />\n<br />\n你呀媽個間本身係人地家族企業另計<br />\n入面本身就多廢物"},{"pid":"3602f3f49d766c88ba064c34e37a71ff5f34a69d","tid":1398502,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:26:41.000Z","msg":"重點係份工幫你儲到cv<br />\n 其他工冇人知你靠呀媽先入到去逗呢份糧<br />\n當係踏腳石你之後嘅路都好行好多<br />\n閒言閒語受一年半載冇乜所謂啦"},{"pid":"f39effb667992053e0262b3fbfd90948d88580ea","tid":1398502,"uid":294052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:28:37.000Z","msg":"若要生活好 咪撚信老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ef9d23593d8a3580d4c09c00747f852d4dda8d","tid":1398502,"uid":7673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"75ecad2bdc228177c3ae05eb2fc65d4c2f3327f2","tid":1398502,"uid":128472,"like":6,"dislike":75,"score":-69,"quote":{"pid":"ef69821ef344dc1627e0938b2a3adbdd37705d91","tid":1398502,"uid":62755,"like":479,"dislike":0,"score":479,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T21:38:57.000Z","msg":"太子爺幫daddy打工算唔算群腳？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T21:41:16.000Z","msg":"唔算掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />間公司係你daddy開？應該係家族生意，啲員工都唔敢笑9你。但我老母只係個打工仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:28:47.000Z","msg":"打工仔....打工仔對你咁好"},{"pid":"2757a9ed241c92cb93a542df0e6c58231f680aae","tid":1398502,"uid":36670,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"772cba5f14adba4c4faeccf5a2e3223a9ee3b719","tid":1398502,"uid":56204,"like":13,"dislike":53,"score":-40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T00:13:03.000Z","msg":"舊公司有條仔做緊audit assistant，得個中七畢業，其他人全部accounting degree，佢老母係hr manager，我地日日笑9佢裙腳仔，由佢自生自滅，無人同佢食飯講野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:42:56.000Z","msg":"有degree仲唔入big4做，我會笑返你轉頭囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bbc783f37784ad8ad65c4f324a4186505775e9","tid":1398502,"uid":169758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:45:37.000Z","msg":"冇人叫你開咪話俾人知你老母係同事"},{"pid":"1dc03dbe8bd363050d8e6ad5e47bfacf216de205","tid":1398502,"uid":283504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4df5d8bbcff53bf10d75b6aa41c504ceee592a8d","tid":1398502,"uid":9214,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T23:59:41.000Z","msg":"做一年之後走<br />\n拎住個價再搵工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:48:01.000Z","msg":"+1"},{"pid":"c2d025fe4f40cbc00c5417e9eb4937a6b37459d5","tid":1398502,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:53:26.000Z","msg":"比我就肯定唔會做<br />\n<br />\n你自己就睇情況<br />\n你覺得冇嘢就冇嘢啦"},{"pid":"ca44b95bfd3a7a975f9a33519261dc6d28e92a7c","tid":1398502,"uid":37600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:00:03.000Z","msg":"俾人笑下多5k 老閪都做<br />\n你估而加返工係返學咩<br />\n俾人杯有咩所謂 收工又係一條好漢"},{"pid":"100cad6b1c5687f790889f2cc88ec60e6abcb696","tid":1398502,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e43a0c697729dedb82f73180866aad163035f489","tid":1398502,"uid":81172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9dc7de614bc0496ee72660fa7ac89b60c2664854","tid":1398502,"uid":203251,"like":368,"dislike":2,"score":366,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T21:39:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2019 fresh grad未開始搵工。咁老母今日同我講話佢公司有個人就走，就問我要唔要入去做。個職位本身淨係請有經驗既人，所以其實我都好驚入咗去但根本冇能力勝任，會唔心安理得同埋影衰老母。加上同自己阿媽同一間公司，所有嘢好似會變得好奇怪同柒（雖然唔同department）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lunch一齊/唔一齊食好奇怪，當私人時間同自己阿媽傾公事又係唔知想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋入到去應該會有閒言閒語（已經想像到比人恥笑靠母幹、裙腳仔）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">但個職位應該幾好pay，如果我用自己能力喺出面搵應該會少成<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5k</span>人工。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請問如果係你哋會點揀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老閪都做，到時發現冇能力/唔掂先走"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:02:40.000Z","msg":"發現無能力都要做 反正帶左老母返工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088d05358af4ba04a3995c83e6f0baf5c2aa2895","tid":1398502,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:04:41.000Z","msg":"做 番工有人蝦你即該去搵老母"},{"pid":"e5ca6154196d02321e2dbd181da31c60d447ff5f","tid":1398502,"uid":160348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:14:26.000Z","msg":"雖然唔想推啲冇用po阻住有需要資訊，但<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">老幾都做咗先，攞呢個高人工R出面第二啲offer</span>"},{"pid":"a7f13d88a12e78637dc3ebd3212f99e99ffbcfca","tid":1398502,"uid":164264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:32:16.000Z","msg":"大公司定細公司？大公司既話覺得冇所謂<br />\n我都試過番intern番呀媽公司<br />\n入到去扮唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呀媽啲friend識我既都好識做，last day先相認"},{"pid":"5ffb47376a3b12b433d2d60230284c86c3d202ff","tid":1398502,"uid":41791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:37:15.000Z","msg":"其實好正常 唔洗諗太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d996594691b69ee5f37da87c28d10ebe5a3dffed","tid":1398502,"uid":292509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"兩睇啦<br />\n之前同老母同一公司做野<br />\n可能我d同事 佢都識<br />\n所以多左野講 關係好左<br />\n如果驚影響自己屋企人咪努力d <br />\n同一間公司冇問題既<br />\n做好自己 人地就冇閒言閒語"},{"pid":"1643057e11aa70c48799d415f61e7e84501e9fb4","tid":1398502,"uid":95761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:39:40.000Z","msg":"有個朋友條仔就係幫自己老母間公司做野<br />\n人工都係fresh grad價<br />\n跟住條女成日同佢嘈<br />\n話如果冇左佢老母<br />\n條仔喺出面就好似冇自己作為<br />\n唔想佢靠佢屋企人<br />\n我個朋友就覺得好冇安全感"},{"pid":"c6633f4dfb39902e9c5a09fb2e97019c71d833b2","tid":1398502,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf655f7fa4ddf14b48329e7688166082ac3e6b39","tid":1398502,"uid":9726,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ef69821ef344dc1627e0938b2a3adbdd37705d91","tid":1398502,"uid":62755,"like":479,"dislike":0,"score":479,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T21:38:57.000Z","msg":"太子爺幫daddy打工算唔算群腳？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T01:55:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:40:49.000Z","msg":"你要奶埋袋底先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177c052e14dc8f62095f248697d8d7f25fc8919c","tid":1398502,"uid":95761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1643057e11aa70c48799d415f61e7e84501e9fb4","tid":1398502,"uid":95761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:39:40.000Z","msg":"有個朋友條仔就係幫自己老母間公司做野<br />\n人工都係fresh grad價<br />\n跟住條女成日同佢嘈<br />\n話如果冇左佢老母<br />\n條仔喺出面就好似冇自己作為<br />\n唔想佢靠佢屋企人<br />\n我個朋友就覺得好冇安全感"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:41:08.000Z","msg":"仲要個女仔fd同佢老母唔多夾<br />\n佢條仔永遠都俾佢老母控制住咁<br />\n跟住個女仔就覺得佢唔重視佢(下刪1000字）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以都幾麻煩"},{"pid":"1309a6c0092deecc1bd0431ef272f5b95ea3b86d","tid":1398502,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef69821ef344dc1627e0938b2a3adbdd37705d91","tid":1398502,"uid":62755,"like":479,"dislike":0,"score":479,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T21:38:57.000Z","msg":"太子爺幫daddy打工算唔算群腳？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:42:14.000Z","msg":"So?佢地妒忌自己無啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\